name: FossProject
tagline: A website for a Rubber Technology Business
body:
This is a starter project for our FOSS class in college under our undergraduate course in Computer Science.    
It is a website for a business in Rubber Technology.

Our mailing list is projectfoss@googlegroups.com  
You can reach us on our IRC channel #foss_project at [freenode](https://webchat.freenode.net)  
Click [here](https://github.com/zeus9/FossProject/wiki) to view this project's Wiki.     

The people involved in contributing to the project are  
[Sambhav Jain](https://github.com/zeus9/)  
[Siddarth Jawahar](https://github.com/basusisa/)  
[Basil Gafoor](https://github.com/basilgafoor/)  
[Sundarrajan](https://github.com/sundarg4/)  
  
Our guide is [Mr.Dayanand V](https://github.com/dayanandv)
